45:17.147 --> 45:19.048
Man:
Elsa mars.

45:19.050 --> 45:20.983
We have a warrant
to search the premises

45:20.985 --> 45:22.318
For evidence pertaining
to the disappearance

45:22.320 --> 45:24.020
Of detective
robert bunch.

45:24.022 --> 45:26.856
On what grounds, officer?

45:26.858 --> 45:31.060
We received an anonymous tip.

45:31.062 --> 45:32.895
We have reasons to believe
he was murdered here.

45:34.198 --> 45:36.899
Which one of these tents
belongs to dell toledo?

45:36.901 --> 45:38.000
What?

45:38.002 --> 45:39.502
That one over there.

45:39.504 --> 45:40.903
Turn it upside down!
Dell: Wait a minute.

45:40.905 --> 45:42.071
What the hell
is going on here?

45:42.073 --> 45:43.906
Hey, hold on, pal.

45:43.908 --> 45:46.175
We only just got here
a couple of days ago.

45:46.177 --> 45:47.176
We haven't
done anything.

45:47.178 --> 45:48.177
Shut your trap.

45:48.179 --> 45:49.345
Desiree:
Dell! Dell!

45:49.347 --> 45:50.880
Colquitt: We already
got an earful

45:50.882 --> 45:53.850
About what a boy scout
you were, from chicago pd.

45:53.852 --> 45:55.918
I'm telling you--
there's nothing in there.

46:01.525 --> 46:03.526
Why are you so smug?

46:03.528 --> 46:06.095
You're the one with
the guilty look on your face.

46:06.097 --> 46:07.897
Nothing in the trailer, sir.

46:07.899 --> 46:10.933
Colquitt: Nobody moves a muscle
until we search every tent here!

46:10.935 --> 46:12.268
Tear this place apart!

46:19.376 --> 46:21.444
Is this what
guilt looks like?

46:22.880 --> 46:26.048
Tragic, isn't it,
when a plan breaks down?

46:26.050 --> 46:27.383
Dell: <i>Where do you think</i>
<i>you're going?</i>

46:27.385 --> 46:29.118
Dot:
¶ what I need

46:29.120 --> 46:32.021
¶ is a good defense

46:33.557 --> 46:35.558
Dell:
Jimmy...

46:35.560 --> 46:38.728
There was no way the cops
were ever gonna find

46:38.730 --> 46:40.997
What you left behind
in my trailer.

46:41.899 --> 46:43.466
Officer:
Found it, sir!

46:43.468 --> 46:45.468
(whimpering):
Meep-meep... Meep...

46:47.471 --> 46:49.906
Meep...
(whimpering)

46:49.908 --> 46:51.307
It was under his bed roll.

46:56.480 --> 46:58.314
This is detective bunch's badge.

46:58.316 --> 47:01.918
I'm shocked, officer.

47:01.920 --> 47:03.319
Shocked.

47:06.423 --> 47:09.425
Take this freak to the station.

47:09.427 --> 47:11.494
(meep whimpering)

47:12.596 --> 47:14.664
(engine starts)

47:39.122 --> 47:40.857
(whimpering)

47:46.997 --> 47:49.999
(door creaking shut)

47:50.001 --> 47:52.368
Doyle: I'm telling you,
there's no way this guy

47:52.370 --> 47:53.636
Is the mastermind
behind everything.

47:53.638 --> 47:55.137
He had the badge.

47:55.139 --> 47:56.305
Even if he didn't
kill those people,

47:56.307 --> 47:57.974
He knows who did.
A night in the tank,

47:57.976 --> 48:01.043
You'll name names.

48:01.045 --> 48:03.379
Get a load of this.

48:05.983 --> 48:08.050
(whimpering)

48:11.822 --> 48:13.890
Inmate:
So you're the big, scary killer?

48:17.027 --> 48:19.328
You like to diddle
little kiddies, you sick freak?

48:19.330 --> 48:21.397
(whimpering)

48:24.501 --> 48:26.168
Greaser: I heard they
found the toy store owner

48:26.170 --> 48:28.070
With his fingers missing.

48:28.072 --> 48:30.006
How about I rip yours off,
one by one?

48:30.008 --> 48:31.908
(shrieking):
Meep!

48:31.910 --> 48:33.542
Meep!

48:33.544 --> 48:35.011
Meep!

48:35.013 --> 48:37.079
(echoing):
Meep.

48:52.896 --> 48:54.297
(whispering):
Wake up.

48:57.768 --> 48:59.268
I came to congratulate you

48:59.270 --> 49:01.737
On your triumph tonight.

49:01.739 --> 49:04.206
They loved her, not me.

49:04.208 --> 49:07.576
I kept trying to run
off the stage.

49:07.578 --> 49:10.212
I felt so embarrassed.

49:10.214 --> 49:13.082
And now she's really mad at me.

49:13.084 --> 49:14.717
She's mad at you?
Mm-hmm.

49:14.719 --> 49:15.918
Oh. (chuckles)

49:15.920 --> 49:19.121
She deliberately eclipsed you.

49:19.123 --> 49:21.590
She made you feel like shite.

49:21.592 --> 49:23.960
I thought I would be good.

49:27.064 --> 49:29.432
I thought all I needed
was an audience.

49:29.434 --> 49:33.135
And it would all come together.

49:34.805 --> 49:36.906
I'm such

49:36.908 --> 49:38.574
A stupid fool.

49:38.576 --> 49:40.776
That's how she
wants you to feel.

49:40.778 --> 49:43.079
These people get
their confidence

49:43.081 --> 49:47.650
From feeding off others'
self-doubt.

49:50.921 --> 49:53.789
You talking in your sleep?

49:53.791 --> 49:56.325
No, it's elsa.

49:56.327 --> 49:59.328
She came to congratulate us.

49:59.330 --> 50:00.663
Well, tell her thanks.

50:00.665 --> 50:02.531
We're sleeping.

50:07.437 --> 50:09.438
It's like she's become
another person.

50:09.440 --> 50:10.606
Oh.

50:10.608 --> 50:13.976
Really, truly, anyone can see...

50:13.978 --> 50:17.313
You are the star,

50:17.315 --> 50:19.015
My angel.

50:19.017 --> 50:21.050
(giggling softly)

50:26.123 --> 50:27.857
But that one,

50:27.859 --> 50:29.992
She has a dark soul.

50:29.994 --> 50:31.027
Mm-hmm.

50:33.463 --> 50:35.031
She wants what you have,

50:35.033 --> 50:37.700
And she knows how to take it.

50:41.371 --> 50:44.106
But you mustn't allow it.

50:52.516 --> 50:54.583
You mustn't allow it.

50:56.887 --> 50:58.921
My angel.

51:35.192 --> 51:37.259
(sighs)

51:43.533 --> 51:45.167
(coughs)

51:48.605 --> 51:51.340
Son, what are you doing?

51:54.377 --> 51:56.445
What's it look like I'm doing?

51:58.949 --> 52:00.916
My sweet boy.

52:00.918 --> 52:02.885
What's wrong?

52:02.887 --> 52:04.887
I've never seen you
take a drink before.

52:04.889 --> 52:06.388
I've always been
so proud of you,

52:06.390 --> 52:08.424
Staying away from this shit.

52:08.426 --> 52:11.260
You're such an example
to the others.

52:11.262 --> 52:13.329
I can't help the others.

52:18.401 --> 52:20.469
(sniffles)
they took meep.

52:23.140 --> 52:25.207
Meep.

52:28.145 --> 52:30.212
He didn't do anything.

52:32.249 --> 52:33.782
It's my fault.

52:33.784 --> 52:34.984
That's nonsense.

52:34.986 --> 52:36.986
You had nothing to do with that.

52:36.988 --> 52:40.055
The police had no right,
roughing you up like that.

52:42.959 --> 52:44.927
I just wanted him gone.

52:44.929 --> 52:48.130
Meep?

52:48.132 --> 52:49.431
Dell.

52:49.433 --> 52:52.434
He's bad news.

52:52.436 --> 52:54.603
More'n that, jimmy,

52:54.605 --> 52:56.438
I want you to stay away
from that man.

52:56.440 --> 52:58.307
You hear me?

52:58.309 --> 52:59.308
(thumps stage)

52:59.310 --> 53:00.609
(groans)

53:00.611 --> 53:03.112
I gotta tell them.

53:03.114 --> 53:04.980
I gotta get him out.

53:04.982 --> 53:06.949
No, no, jimmy...
Yeah, I've gotta tell them...

53:06.951 --> 53:09.785
That's easier said than done.
...He can get out!

53:09.787 --> 53:10.986
The bastard has
signed a contract.

53:10.988 --> 53:12.188
Jimmy!

53:13.990 --> 53:15.291
Not dell!

53:15.293 --> 53:17.259
Meep!

53:19.696 --> 53:22.798
He's not gonna be able to spend
the night in jail, mom.

53:22.800 --> 53:24.800
He's not tough.

53:24.802 --> 53:26.969
(panting)

53:26.971 --> 53:30.639
He's just weird.

53:30.641 --> 53:33.509
I gotta...

53:33.511 --> 53:36.212
I have to tell them everything.

53:38.982 --> 53:40.382
(sighs)

53:40.384 --> 53:42.084
I'm sorry.

53:44.821 --> 53:46.755
Tell who what?

53:48.558 --> 53:49.825
Jimmy?

53:49.827 --> 53:52.194
Jimmy!

53:52.196 --> 53:54.463
(truck approaching)

54:17.687 --> 54:19.989
(screaming)

54:24.894 --> 54:26.962
(jimmy sobbing)

